==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*πρῶτος / prōtos / pro'-tos

===Etymology===
*Contracted superlative of [[πρό]] {{GG|4253}}; [[foremost]] (in time, place, order or importance): 

===Adjective===
'''πρῶτος'''

# [[before]], [[beginning]], [[best]], [[chief]] (-est), first (of all), [[former]].

